description: Enjoy a quick and easy meal with this express veg stir fry recipe. Using just five ingredients, this budget-friendly dish is a winner.
keywords: Vegetable stir-fry,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Halal,Vegetarian,Vegan,Low fat,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Express Veg Stir Fry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Prepare noodles following instructions. Set aside.
Heat a large wok, add curry paste and vegetables, stir fry for 23 minutes. Place 1/4 cup vegetable stock in a small bowl or jug add cornflour and mix well.
Add remaining stock to the vegetable stir fry, bring to the boil, add cornflour mixture stirring until sauce thickens. Add drained noodles and stir to combine.
